data.title: LS2 PAC
data.text:
Log in with either your Library Card Number or EZ Login

For accounts created after January 1st, 2023, the default PIN is 'CHANGEME'. The PINs for all accounts created prior to 2023 were reset to 'changeme' as part of our catalog migration. Please be aware that all log-in information is case sensitive. Cards begin with BLOG, not blog. After you log in for the first time, you can go to your account to update your PIN (1-8 characters), create your own EZ Username and EZ Password to use instead of your library card and library pin, and/or link your library account to your Google account (if you have one).
